---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Thompson Chiropractic Achieved 72% Treatment Completion | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/medical-dental/specialty-practices" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Specialty Practices
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          How Thompson Chiropractic Achieved 72% Treatment Completion
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Hamilton wellness practice transformed patient outcomes with automated follow-up systems.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">72%</div>
              <div class="text-violet-100">Treatment Completion</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">2.1x</div>
              <div class="text-violet-100">Patient Referrals</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">58%</div>
              <div class="text-violet-100">No-Show Reduction</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$47K</div>
              <div class="text-violet-100">Monthly Revenue</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Practice:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Thompson Chiropractic & Wellness</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Hamilton, ON</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Type:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Chiropractic & wellness</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Size:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">2 chiropractors, 1 RMT</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Dr. Kevin Thompson's practice had a 35% treatment plan completion rate—patients started care but dropped off before finishing. No-shows ran 18%. Referrals were sporadic. New patient growth stalled. Revenue remained flat despite excellent clinical outcomes.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented treatment plan follow-up sequences, multi-touch appointment reminders, post-treatment referral requests, and year-end benefits campaigns to capture unused insurance coverage.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Treatment completion hit 72%. Referrals grew 2.1x. No-shows dropped 58%. Monthly revenue increased $47K. Patients now finish their care plans and recommend friends.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-violet-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "Patients used to drop off after 3-4 visits. Now they complete their full plans because automated follow-ups keep them accountable and engaged."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">— Dr. Kevin Thompson, Owner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-purple-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Improve Treatment Compliance?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-violet-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
